## Path Aliases Reference

| Alias | Path |
|---|---|
| `@src` | `src/` |
| `@layouts` | `src/layouts/` |
| `@shared` | `src/shared/` |
| `@utils` | `src/utils/` |
| `@services` | `src/services/` |
| `@sass` | `src/sass/` |
| `@data` | `src/data/` |
| `@controllers` | `src/controllers/` |

---

## Key Conventions

- SCSS color tokens: `$french-violet`, `$ufo-green`, `$light-violet`, `$dark-violet`
- SCSS mixins: `flexConfig()`, `respond-to()`, `text-gradient`
- Dark mode: `.dark {}` class on `<html>` element; use `.dark { .component { ... } }` pattern in SCSS
- Cookie: `accessToken` (HttpOnly, SameSite=Strict), signed with `SECRET_KEY` env var
- Comment proxy: client -> `/api/comments/replies` -> WPGraphQL (never direct from browser)
- Learning paths: `/languages/[slug]/module/[moduleSlug]` two-level nested routing
